  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FinTech_AuthVault和FinTech_FraudDetection之间的连接流程画一个图。核心场景是客户端发起请求，经过FraudDetection验证后决定是继续处理还是丢弃。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我打算用两个子图来区分客户端和服务端。客户端这边我放FinTech_AuthVault、FinTech_LedgerService、FinTech_FraudDetection和FinTech_PaymentGateway这几个节点，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C4",
        "C5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但注意FinTech_AuthVault在客户端其实出现了两次，一个是入口C1，一个是C3作为中间节点。另外FraudDetection在客户端是C4，主要用于风险预检。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Client子图画出来：C1和C3都是FinTech_AuthVault，C2是LedgerService，C4是FraudDetection，C5是PaymentGateway。现在画Server子图，FraudDetection作为容器名，里面放S1到S6。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server",
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "S6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Server这边S1是LedgerService的入口，S2需要做成判断节点，用菱形表示，它是TransactionQueue。S3和S5分别是两个分支的出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，S2是菱形判断节点，标签是FinTech_TransactionQueue。那S3、S4、S5、S6分别对应什么？S4是PaymentGateway，S6是AuthVault对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "S6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。S3也是TransactionQueue，S4是PaymentGateway，S5回到LedgerService，S6是AuthVault用于连接关闭流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "S6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "节点都建好了。现在开始连主线：C1到C2到C3，然后C3连到S1，这是请求的入口路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "S1这里要做校验，如果invalid就直接Drop到FraudDetection。通过的话进入S2的判断逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "Drop",
        "S2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，S1分出两条线：一条标invalid指向Drop节点，另一条正常连到S2。",
